<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your <%= company_name %> Order is on its Way!</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #292524;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
    }
    .email-wrapper {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
    }
    
    /* Main Container */
    .main-container {
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 3px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 1px 2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      border: 1px solid #fed7aa;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .container-header {
      padding: 20px 24px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #fed7aa;
      background-color: #fff7ed;
    }
    
    .container-title {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #9a3412;
      margin: 0 0 4px 0;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }
    
    .container-subtitle {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #ea580c;
      margin: 0;
      font-weight: 400;
    }
    
    .container-content {
      padding: 24px;
    }
    
    .brand-logo {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #ea580c;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .content-section {
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    
    .content-section p {
      margin: 0 0 16px 0;
      color: #374151;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    
    .content-section ul {
      margin: 16px 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
      color: #374151;
    }
    
    .content-section li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    
    /* Shipping Details Card */
    .shipping-details {
      background-color: #f0fdf4;
      border: 1px solid #22c55e;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    
    .shipping-details h3 {
      color: #15803d;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 0 0 16px 0;
    }
    
    .shipping-details p {
      margin: 8px 0;
      color: #166534;
    }
    
    .shipping-details strong {
      color: #15803d;
    }
    
    /* Tracking Info */
    .tracking-info {
      background-color: #fef3c7;
      border: 1px solid #f59e0b;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .tracking-info h3 {
      color: #92400e;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 0 0 16px 0;
    }
    
    .tracking-number {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #b45309;
      background-color: #fffbeb;
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      border: 1px solid #fbbf24;
      margin: 12px 0;
    }
    
    /* Order Summary */
    .order-summary {
      background-color: #f0f9ff;
      border: 1px solid #60a5fa;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    
    .order-summary h3 {
      color: #1e40af;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 0 0 16px 0;
    }
    
    .order-summary p {
      margin: 8px 0;
      color: #1e3a8a;
    }
    
    .order-summary strong {
      color: #1e40af;
    }
    
    .order-items {
      background-color: #f8fafc;
      border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 16px 0;
    }
    
    .order-items ul {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }
    
    .order-items li {
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      color: #475569;
    }
    
    /* CTA Button */
    .btn-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }
    
    .btn-primary {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #ea580c;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 14px;
      text-align: center;
      transition: background-color 0.15s ease-in-out;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      margin-right: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    
    .btn-primary:hover {
      background-color: #dc2626;
    }
    
    .btn-secondary {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #6b7280;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 14px;
      text-align: center;
      transition: background-color 0.15s ease-in-out;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      margin-right: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    
    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background-color: #374151;
    }
    
    /* Delivery Timeline */
    .delivery-timeline {
      background-color: #f3f4f6;
      border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    
    .delivery-timeline h3 {
      color: #374151;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 0 0 16px 0;
    }
    
    .delivery-timeline ul {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }
    
    .delivery-timeline li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    
    .footer {
      margin-top: 32px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    
    .footer-link {
      color: #ea580c;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    
    .footer-link:hover {
      color: #dc2626;
    }
    
    .signature {
      margin-top: 24px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #374151;
    }
    
    .signature-name {
      color: #ea580c;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    
    .status-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 4px 8px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      background-color: #d1fae5;
      color: #065f46;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="main-container">
      <div class="container-header">
        <div class="brand-logo">üç™ <%= company_name %></div>
        <h1 class="container-title">Your Order Has Shipped!</h1>
        <p class="container-subtitle">Your delicious cookies are on their way to you</p>
      </div>

      <div class="container-content">
        <div class="content-section">
          <% if @order %>
            <p>Hello <%= @order.user&.display_name || @order.customer_name %>,</p>
          <% else %>
            <p>Hello valued customer,</p>
          <% end %>
          
          <p>Great news! Your <%= company_name %> order has been shipped and is on its way to you. We know you're excited to taste our authentic Filipino crinkle cookies!</p>
          
          <% if @order %>
            <div class="shipping-details">
              <h3>üì¶ Shipping Details</h3>
              <p><strong>Order Number:</strong> #<%= @order.id %></p>
              <p><strong>Ship Date:</strong> <%= Date.current.strftime('%B %d, %Y') %></p>
              <p><strong>Estimated Delivery:</strong> <%= (Date.current + 3.days).strftime('%B %d, %Y') %> - <%= (Date.current + 5.days).strftime('%B %d, %Y') %></p>
              <p><strong>Status:</strong> <span class="status-badge">Shipped</span></p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="tracking-info">
              <h3>üìç Track Your Package</h3>
              <p>Your tracking number is:</p>
              <div class="tracking-number">MG<%= @order.id %>-<%= Date.current.strftime('%Y%m%d') %></div>
              <p style="margin-top: 16px; color: #b45309;">Use this number to track your package with our shipping partner.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="order-summary">
              <h3>üìã Order Summary</h3>
              <p><strong>Order Date:</strong> <%= @order.created_at.strftime('%B %d, %Y') %></p>
              <p><strong>Total:</strong> $<%= number_with_precision(@order.total_price, precision: 2) %></p>
              
              <div class="order-items">
                <h4>üç™ Items Shipped:</h4>
                <ul>
                  <% @order.line_items.each do |item| %>
                    <li><%= item.quantity %>x <%= item.purchasable.name %> - $<%= number_with_precision(item.price, precision: 2) %></li>
                  <% end %>
                </ul>
              </div>
              
              <p><strong>Shipping Address:</strong></p>
              <p style="white-space: pre-line; margin: 8px 0;"><%= @order.address %></p>
            </div>
          <% end %>
          
          <div class="delivery-timeline">
            <h3>üìÖ What to Expect</h3>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Today:</strong> Your cookies have left our kitchen and are in transit</li>
              <li><strong>1-2 days:</strong> Package is processed through shipping facilities</li>
              <li><strong>3-5 days:</strong> Delivery to your doorstep</li>
              <li><strong>Enjoy!</strong> Fresh, authentic Filipino crinkle cookies await you</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="btn-container">
            <a href="#" class="btn-primary">Track Your Package</a>
            <a href="<%= root_url %>" class="btn-secondary">Shop More Cookies</a>
          </div>
          
          <p>Your cookies are carefully packaged to ensure they arrive fresh and delicious. If you have any questions about your shipment, please don't hesitate to contact us at <strong><%= company_email %></strong>.</p>
          
          <p>We can't wait for you to taste our authentic Filipino treats! Don't forget to share your experience with us on social media.</p>
          
          <div class="signature">
            <p>Thank you for choosing <%= company_name %>!</p>
            <p class="signature-name">The <%= company_name %> Team</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
          <p>This email was sent to <%= @order&.email || 'your email' %> because your order has been shipped.</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 20px;">
            &copy; <%= Date.current.year %> <%= company_name %>. All rights reserved.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 